🔷 Algorithm

Step-by-step Algorithm:

Start
Declare variables:
Team name
Matches played (M)
Wins (W), Losses (L)
Points (P)
Input number of teams (n)
Repeat for each team (i = 1 to n):
Input team name
Input matches played (M)
Input wins (W)
Calculate losses:
→ L = M − W
Calculate points:
→ P = W × 2
Store all team details
Sort teams based on points in descending order
Display points table with ranking
Stop
